timing_rcdb_a...ismatch_option(25.10)    timing_rcdb_a...ismatch_option(25.10)

Name
       timing_rcdb_allow_mismatch_option

Syntax
       timing_rcdb_allow_mismatch_option {true | false}

       Default: true

       Disables errors while reading boundary models.

       When  set to true, the software disables errors when reading the bound-
       ary model RCBD for cases where the contents do not match  the  boundary
       model netlist.

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

